      • StringArrayTableModel

        public StringArrayTableModel(int columns,
                             String... colnames)

        Create a new table cell model with the given data.

        Parameters:
        columns - The number of columns
        colnames - The cell data. The first columns values are interpreted as the column names, and the rest is row data.
